---
title: Hawaiian Loco Moco with Mushroom Gravy
description: A classic Hawaiian staple! Crisp pan-fried beef patties sit atop steamed white rice and umami-packed mushroom gravy crowns this masterpiece! It's an island favourite! Add a fried egg over top for an extra creamy punch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/loco-moco-hawaien-64dfd67b.jpg
